
********************************************************`
This is Dynetix Utility framework
********************************************************`


1. To install the framework, include in your Podfile
   for an IOS project:

    pod 'DynetixUtility', :git => 'https://github.com/tchan1010/DynetixUtility.git', :tag => '1.0.2'

2.  Then link your app with the  DynetixUtility.framework 


3. In your app's Swift source files, add:

   import DynetixUtility

4. Call any of these functions:

   showMessage( caller: UIViewController,  title : String,  msg : String,
                         doEmail : Bool = false,  Image : UIImage? = nil)

   sendEmail( caller: UIViewController,  subject : String,  msg : String,  image : UIImage? )

   Note: to send email, the 'caller' should be a MFMailComposeViewControllerDelegate
